title: Historic bitter crab syndrome monitoring dataset
description: This dataset contains sample collection data for all majid, cancrid and lithodid decapods collected by the NOAA AFSC Pathobiology group from 1978 to 2013
keywords: bitter crab syndrome, Bering Sea, Gulf of Alaska, tanner crab, snow crab, red king crab
geographicDescription: LME's: Bering Sea, GOA, Arctic, Beaufort Sea, Aleutian Islands, Atlantic Coast/Newfoundland
